1. *Štiti* ga od zime. (It protects him from the winter.)
2. On voli da *štiti* svoju porodicu. (He likes to protect his family.)
3. Naši planovi su bili da *štite* zemlju. (Our plans were to protect the land.)
4. On veoma ceni svoje zdravlje koje mu *štiti* lekari. (He highly values his health which is protected by doctors.)
5. Ona je *štitila* svoju decu od nezgodnih situacija. (She was protecting her children from awkward situations.)
6. Uradili smo sve kako bismo *štitili* našu planetu. (We did everything to protect our planet.)